ing: 1 (16 ounce) container frozen whipped topping, thawed
1 (5 ounce) package instant vanilla pudding mix
des: "This is a very creamy and yummy vanilla pumpkin dip that is served with graham crackers.  I like the cinnamon graham crackers best, but you can decide for yourself."
ins: In a large bowl, mix together instant vanilla pudding mix, pumpkin and pumpkin pie spice. Fold in the thawed frozen whipped topping. Chill in the refrigerator until serving.
